commit message: Fixed some index issues in Comments and Submissions
More powerful Multireddit editor, Can now add un-subscribed subs to Multireddits
Added more options to the sidebar under Profile, Made clicking Profile in sidebar go straight to the Profile activity, Start of Streamable support
Added support for Streamable.com content piggybacking off of the GifView activity
Added animations to the flip icons in the drawer
Changed the icon in drawables to the new icon
Lots of bug fixes, Updated icon, Fixed KitKat crash
